flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Write Code]
    B --> C[Code Review]
    C --> D{Is Code Approved?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Run Automated Tests]
    D -- No --> B
    E --> F{Do Tests Pass?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Check Code Coverage]
    F -- No --> H[Fix Issues]
    H --> E
    G --> I{Is Coverage Above Threshold?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Merge Code]
    I -- No --> K[Increase Coverage]
    K --> E
    J --> L[Deploy to Production]
    L --> M[Monitor Code Quality]
    M --> N[End]